 - 100% PROTECTION: 11D Big Curved Edge Full Glue, Clarity and High-Response Touch Preserve, Fast exhaust, 9H hardness for maximum protection. It protects your phone from high-impact drops, keys in your pockets, metal objects in your bags, and other day-to-day scratches.
 

 - DESIGN: 9H hardness and Ultrathin-0.3mm thickness which is reliable and resilient and promises full compatibility with touchscreen sensitivity. Due to rapid exhaustion, the installation is easy, giving a perfect alignment without bubbles.

 - ANTI-SHATTER: If broken, the glass will break into small parts but stay in one piece, making it safer for the glass screen of your phone. Highly durable and scratch-resistant - surface hardness 9H.
 

 - OLEOPHOBIC COATING: Makes the Screen Protector resistant to oil particles, which in turn makes it resistive to fingerprints and protects your phone against sweat and oil residue from fingerprints, keeping your phone screen clean with smoother touch, compatible with 3D Touch.

 - A service after ordering screen guard that we provide is our rider will install the screen guard for you at your door step. So you don't have to worry about how will it be done.
 

 - 100% PROTECTION: 11D Big Curved Edge Full Glue, Clarity and High-Response Touch Preserve, Fast exhaust, 9H hardness for maximum protection. It protects your phone from high-impact drops, keys in your pockets, metal objects in your bags, and other day-to-day scratches.
 

 - DESIGN: 9H hardness and Ultrathin-0.3mm thickness which is reliable and resilient and promises full compatibility with touchscreen sensitivity. Due to rapid exhaustion, the installation is easy, giving a perfect alignment without bubbles.
 

 - VISIBILITY: This tempered glass Screen Protector is a chemical processed real glass. It features high HD transparency, high sensitivity, and a delicate touch feeling.
 

 - ANTI-SHATTER: If broken, the glass will break into small parts but stay in one piece, making it safer for the glass screen of your phone. Highly durable and scratch-resistant - surface hardness 9H.
 

 - OLEOPHOBIC COATING: Makes the Screen Protector resistant to oil particles, which in turn makes it resistive to fingerprints and protects your phone against sweat and oil residue from fingerprints, keeping your phone screen clean with smoother touch, compatible with 3D Touch.

MOBILE_HOLDERS_AND_MORE.TITLE: 3.5" LED Selfie Ring Light with Phone Holder | Flexible Arm Desk | 3 Color 10 Brightness Level
MOBILE_HOLDERS_AND_MORE.ProductDescription:
3 LIGHT MODES & 10 BRIGHTNESS LEVELS: Dimmable 12W LED Desk Ring Light with 3 Lighting Modes: Warm Light (3000K), Warm–White Light (4500K) and White Light (6500K). Each Lighting Mode has 10 Adjustable Brightness to Choose. Built-in Controller Easy to Power On/Off and Switch to the Lighting Mode to Fit Your Various Use.
 EYE-CARING SOFT RING LIGHT: Made with Premium LEDs, offers No-Flickering and No-Dazzling Light, Protect your Eyesight and Reduce your Eye Strain while using. This Ring Light provide Soft Adequate Supplement Lighting can Work Perfect as Selfie/ Makeup Lighting or Computer Lighting for Video Conference, Live-Streaming, Vloging, Zoom Meeting, Reading, etc.
